! $Id: whois_channels,v 1.1 2001/12/08 21:44:10 toast Exp $
Usage: FORMAT WHOIS_CHANNELS <format description>
  Controls how the whois line displaying the channels a user is in appears.

  Valid format characters:
       N          Nick of whois target
       M          The list of channels the whois target is in

  This format has no effect if OLD_WHOIS_FORMAT is ON.

See Also:
  FORMAT WHOIS_ADMIN
  FORMAT WHOIS_AWAY
  FORMAT WHOIS_IDLE
  FORMAT WHOIS_IRCNAME
  FORMAT WHOIS_NSLOOKUP
  FORMAT WHOIS_OPER
  FORMAT WHOIS_SERVER
  FORMAT WHOIS_SIGNON
  FORMAT WHOIS_USERHOST
  FORMAT WHOWAS_USERHOST
  SET OLD_WHOIS_FORMAT
  WHOIS
  WHOWAS
